DARKSOUL.desc: Dark moves deal x1.5 dmg; halves enemy Psychic dmg.

GRENADIER.name: Grenadier
GRENADIER.desc: Ball, bomb, and explosion moves deal x1.25 damage.

SOLOIST.name: Soloist
SOLOIST.desc: 25% stronger if it's your last active Pokemon.

ASSASSIN.name: Assassin
ASSASSIN.desc: Its Physical moves use its Sp. Atk stat.

MYSTICAL.name: Mystical
MYSTICAL.desc: Unchecked Acc moves deal x1.33 dmg and heal 1/2 dmg dealt.

GHOULISH.name: Ghoulish

DRAGONFORCE.name: Dragon Force

SOULFURNACE.name: Soul Furnace

FINISHINGTOUCH.name: Finishing Touch

REFRACTION.name: Refraction

HALCYON.name: Halcyon

TRINITYFORCE.name: Trinity Force

CRUCIBLE.name: Crucible

RIPEN.name: Ripen

GUARDIANCHROMOSOME.name: Guardian Chromosome
